{"tid":315892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"49歲大波美女倒垃圾嗒26歲毒男 叫床聲3個月內惹6宗鄰居投訴","createTime":"2017-07-10T10:45:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-10T11:26:55.000Z","uid":22349,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f0cf4e0847488f464b64b0bc939275c04471e3e6","tid":315892,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T10:45:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170710/large/1499664778_617c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170710%2Flarge%2F1499664778_617c.jpg&h=f3c346c3&s={SIZE}\" /> 49歲瓦萊里奧與26歲男友（左）<br />\n瓦萊里奧的女兒（右）<br />\n<br />\n美國紐約一位大媽與年輕男友翻雲覆雨時，發出的叫床聲引來多位鄰居投訴，為免年紀與男友相若的女兒變自己的代罪羔羊，大媽決定「挺身而出」公開承認自己才是元兇。<br />\n<br />\n49歲的瓦萊里奧（Olga Valerio）是四子之母，5年前外出倒垃圾時，遇上現年26歲的男友。雖然瓦萊里奧年近半百，但與男友性生活仍非常活躍，可憐鄰居們都因她的叫床聲太大而無法入睡，只好向當局投訴。<br />\n<br />\n以2015年為例，當局在短短3個月內就接到鄰居6宗電話投訴，打破以往紀錄。原來瓦萊里奧2人在歡好時，把睡房的窗全打開，震耳欲聾的叫床聲傳出令鄰居無覺好訓。<br />\n<br />\n瓦萊里奧稱鄰居們猜疑女兒是叫床聲的「元兇」，導致她遭調戲，有人甚至大膽上門出價4萬美金（約31萬港元）換取與好一夜歡好。有見及此，瓦萊里奧決定當個負責任的媽媽，主動承認自己才是始作俑者，以捍衞女兒清譽。<br />\n<br />\n瓦萊里奧說：「最初我感到非常尷尬，但如今我覺得還好。我說：『如果我需要交代整件事，我會。』我會為了女兒而做。我從未想過這會發生，但這發生了，我也不知道我們上床有那麼大聲。」<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》/美國《紐約郵報》"},{"pid":"8b9f8d2cb70a5cc79b08155fa3b3d07979a0933b","tid":315892,"uid":90,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T10:47:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 識食"},{"pid":"24d473fd05a392c5ef2e9c944c07a3873bed8038","tid":315892,"uid":24980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T10:50:10.000Z","msg":"大波<br />\n肉地<br />\n金髮<br />\n鬼妹"},{"pid":"6afe794677f6e5016c1a3c0bc2ace666b88bb660","tid":315892,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T10:50:53.000Z","msg":"條仔好似肥豬王"},{"pid":"86543badfa0c8acc0abc194c690fc7564b0a5d20","tid":315892,"uid":13816,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T10:52:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd5155e6385ee3ab45728dbb778f3ce0ace5dc15","tid":315892,"uid":127795,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T10:59:30.000Z","msg":"毒男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7fa7d4e51f64b323a2795921b7e94ebbab6c2af","tid":315892,"uid":35598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T11:00:56.000Z","msg":"母女丼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9459bcc6cce0a0b170e6a71038aceb89078768f1","tid":315892,"uid":40938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T11:06:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自拍同新聞幅相差咁遠既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n盲"},{"pid":"c0cfd1b45af1934be1598352526d464d71a96667","tid":315892,"uid":127381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T11:12:53.000Z","msg":"倒垃圾+50路+母女井<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"870ea15746664e283fc3e27d8145b21137213a25","tid":315892,"uid":62384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T11:15:16.000Z","msg":"大波美國女"},{"pid":"421c82282878f0c7f80f4090bbcc417134d0ed17","tid":315892,"uid":90634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T11:26:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自拍同新聞幅相差咁遠既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n盲</blockquote><br />\n叻唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}